    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10438331>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Distribution map of the type locality of troglomorphic Bisetocreagris species in China. A. B. maomaotou Gao, Wynne et Zhang, 2018 (Maomaotou Cave); B. B. que sp. nov. (Yanggong Cave); C. B. longidigitata sp. nov. (Mao’er Cave); D. B. brevis sp. nov. (Yehu Cave); E. B. aspera sp. nov. (Tu Cave); F. B. jiangi sp. nov. (Anjialin Cave); G. B. tenuipalma sp. nov. (Sanjie Cave); H. B. changbing sp. nov. (Sanyuan and Guanyin caves); I. B. ampla sp. nov. (Hei Cave); J. B. gracilenta Gao et Zhang, 2017 (Shanmu Cave); K. B. guangshanensis Gao et Zhang, 2017 (Guangshan Cave); L. B. chumi sp. nov. (Tufei Cave); M. B. sanmen sp. nov. (Sanmen Cave); N. B. xishui sp. nov. (Dongkoushang Cave); O. B. baozinensis Mahnert et Li, 2016 (Baozi Cave); P. B. chuanensis Mahnert et Li, 2016 (Chuan Cave); Q. B. grandis sp. nov. (Wulibeidadong Cave); R. B. scaura (Mahnert, 2003) (Dahei Cave); S. B. martii (Mahnert, 2003) and B. titania (Mahnert, 2003) (Guoquan Cave); T. B. xiaoensis Li et Liu, 2017 (Xiao Cave); U. B. juanxuae Mahnert et Li, 2016 (Dao Cave); V. B. cavernarum Mahnert et Li, 2016 (Ert Long Cave); W. B. chinacavernicola (Schawaller, 1995) (Xian Nin and Chao-Tian caves)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10438331/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10438450>
    dc:description "FIGURE 57. Bisetocreagris xishui sp. nov., A. Holotype male, dorsal view; B. Paratype female, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10438450/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10438454>
    dc:description "FIGURE 58. Bisetocreagris xishui sp. nov., holotype male (A–F, H–I), female (G). A. Carapace, dorsal view; B. Eye area, lateral view; C. Right chelicera, dorsal view; D. Right chela, lateral view; E. Right pedipalp, dorsal view; F. Male genitalia; G. Female genitalia; H. Right leg I, lateral view; I. Right leg IV, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10438454/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10438462>
    dc:description "FIGURE 59. Bisetocreagris xishui sp. nov., holotype male (A–G, I–M), female (H). A. Carapace, dorsal view; B. Right chelicera, dorsal view; C. Rallum; D. Movable finger of chelicera, showing galea; E. Subterminal tarsal seta; F. Galea; G. Male genitalia, ventral view; H. Female genitalia, ventral view; I. Right chela, dorsal view; J. Right chelal fingers, retrolateral view; K. Right pedipalp, minus chela, dorsal view; L. Right leg I, lateral view; M. Right leg IV, lateral view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm (C‒E), 0.25 mm (B, G‒H), 0.5 mm (A, J), 1 mm (I, K‒M)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10438462/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

